u.s. agricultur secretari warn ec on soy oil tax u.s. agricultur secretari richard lyng warn the european commun yesterday it will face seriou retali if it enact a new tax on product such as u.s. soybean oil . speak at a news confer befor a schedul speech , lyng said he did not think the tax , which is still in the discuss stage , would be approv . he said the u.s. would take seriou retaliatori action becau if implement , the tax would have a consid impact on u.s. farmer .